Message.SourceString: Oh wow, bit of a packrat are we? You're carrying too much right now, come back and chat with me when you've cleared some space from your backpack.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh wow, bit of a packrat are we? You're carrying too much right now, come back and chat with me when you've cleared some space from your backpack.

Message.SourceString: Better not keep him waiting too long, he gets real cranky.
Message.LocalizedString: Better not keep him waiting too long, he gets real cranky.

Message.SourceString: Great work! Runes are the lifeblood of magic, you'll need them to cast spells and use magic staves. A well placed spell can make all the difference.
Message.LocalizedString: Great work! Runes are the lifeblood of magic, you'll need them to cast spells and use magic staves. A well placed spell can make all the difference.

Message.SourceString: Not made the runes yet? You'll need to mine essence from the floating geysers and then craft air and astral runes on a rune altar.
Message.LocalizedString: Not made the runes yet? You'll need to mine essence from the floating geysers and then craft air and astral runes on a rune altar.

Message.SourceString: You'll unlock new spells as you improve your skills. Here, this book should help you toward that. Have a play around with them, you'll find they can be incredibly useful.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll unlock new spells as you improve your skills. Here, this book should help you toward that. Have a play around with them, you'll find they can be incredibly useful.

Message.SourceString: Right, now that you've learned the basics, it's time to get started. The Wise Old Man is waiting for you just outside Bramblemead Village. Follow your compass to find him.
Message.LocalizedString: Right, now that you've learned the basics, it's time to get started. The Wise Old Man is waiting for you just outside Bramblemead Village. Follow your compass to find him.

Message.SourceString: Vannaka was looking for you, mentioned something about fine dining?
Message.LocalizedString: Vannaka was looking for you, mentioned something about fine dining?

Message.SourceString: I think someone is looking for you. Mentioned a task they needed you to complete. Check your map for where to find them.
Message.LocalizedString: I think someone is looking for you. Mentioned a task they needed you to complete. Check your map for where to find them.

Message.SourceString: There are secrets hidden all over Ashenfall, I'm sure of it. Look around, explore, and see what you can find.
